<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css" integrity="sha512-z3gLpd7yknf1YoNbCzqRKc4qyor8gaKU1qmn+CShxbuBusANI9QpRohGBreCFkKxLhei6S9CQXFEbbKuqLg0DA==" crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-4bw+/aepP/YC94hEpVNVgiZdgIC5+VKNBQNGCHeKRQN+PtmoHDEXuppvnDJzQIu9" crossorigin="anonymous">
  <title>Instructions</title>
  <style>
    :root {
      --primary-color: #ffa7e2;
      --secondary-color: #ff75d1;
      --background-gradient-start: #ffd8d8;
      --background-gradient-end: #ffa7e2;
      --text-color: #fff;
      --text-color-alt: #888;
      --hover-shadow-color: #fff;
      --border-color: #ff75d1;
      --dark-color: #ff1db4;
    }

    body {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
      height: 100%;
      width: 100%;
      background: var(--background-gradient-start);
    }

   .container h1 {
    color: #af0075;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 50px;
      font-weight: bolder;
      margin-top: 20px;
      
    }

    .instruct-link{
        font-size: 30px;
        margin: 50px 0;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: var(--dark-color);
    }

    .instruct-sub-head{
        font-size: 35px;
    }
    

    .instructions{
        width: 100%;
    }

    .instruct-head{
        font-size: 38px;
        color: #fd24b5;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .instruct-sub-head{
        color: #ff52c5;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    
    .lead{
        font-size: 25px;
        font-weight: lighter;
    }

    .col-md-7{
        padding: 20px;
    }

    .col-md-7 ul li{
        padding: 5px 0;
    }

    .col-md-5 {
  overflow: hidden;
  
}

.instruct-img {
  height: 100%;
  width: 100%;
      transition: all 0.8s ease-in-out;
}

.col-md-5:hover .instruct-img {
      transform: scale(1.2)
}


     @media (max-width: 890px){
        .container h1{
            font-size: 28px;
        }
        .instruct-link{
            font-size: 18px;
            
        }
        .instruct-head{
            font-size: 22px;
        } 
        .instruct-sub-head{
            font-size: 18px;
        }
        .lead{
            font-size: 16px;
        }

        
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
    
        
    <div class="container instructions">
        <h1>INSTRUCTIONS</h1>
             <h3><a class="instruct-link" href="/">‚Üê Home</a></h3>
        <br>
        <hr>
    
        <div class="row ">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h2 class="instruct-head">First - <span class="instruct-sub-head">Go to Today</span></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Click on the add button to add items in your list.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Now write your task which you want to complete today.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Once it is created then click enter or click on add item to add it into the queue.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">You can add many items as you want in your list.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Once your list completed you can use it to maintain your routine work.</p></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
           <img class="image bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg instruct-img img-fluid mx-auto" src="images/todo.jpg" alt="image">
        </div>
        
        </div>
    
        <hr>
    
        <div class="row ">
            <div class="col-md-7 order-md-2">
                <h2 class="instruct-head">Second - <span class="instruct-sub-head">Go to Work</span></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Click on the add button to add items in your list.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Now write your task or work which you want to complete.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Once it is created then click enter or click on add item to add it into the queue.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">You can add many items as you want in your list.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Once your list completed you can use it to maintain your routine work.</p></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
          <div class="col-md-5 order-md-1">
           <img class=" image bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg instruct-img img-fluid mx-auto" src="images/worklist.jpg" alt="image">
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <hr>
    
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-7">
                <h2 class="instruct-head">Third -  <span class="instruct-sub-head">Check Your List Items.</span></h2>
                <ul>
                    <li> <p class="lead">When you complete your task you can check these checkboxes in order to remember which task is completed and which one is remain to complete.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">This helps you to complete your routine task or work on time as well as it boost you to complete more task.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">If you find any problem regard this applicationyou can notify me.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Thank you for visiting this application.</p></li>
                    <li> <p class="lead">Have a great day..</p></li>
                </ul>
              </div>
          <div class="col-md-5">
           <img class="image bd-placeholder-img bd-placeholder-img-lg instruct-img img-fluid mx-auto" src="images/checklist.jpg" alt="image">
          </div>
        </div>
    
        <hr>
    
      
    
      </div>

  <%- include("partials/footer.ejs") %>
</body>
</html>
